Module kivakit.core.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.resource.path

Class Extension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.resource.path.Extension
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Named
    public class Extension
extends java.lang.Object
implements Named
    A FileName extension, such as ".txt" or ".jar".

    Common extensions are provided as static constants. An extension can also be constructed with parse(String), with or without a dot prefix: 

     Extension.parse(".xyz");
 Extension.parse("xyz");

    Properties

    • name() - The extension as a string
    • codec() - The codec normally used for files with this extension, or the NullCodec if the file is not compressed

    Matching

    • fileMatcher() - A matcher that matches resources with this extension
    • matches(Resource) - True if the given resource has this extension

    Checks

    • endsWith(Extension) - True if this (compound) extension ends with the given extension
    • isArchive() - True if this extensions indicates an archive
    • isExecutable() - True if this extension is normally executable

    Functional Methods

    • gzipped() - This extension with ".gz" on the end
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
